-- Madrid Region May Cut Public Wages Up to 3.5%, El Pais Says
-- B y   A n g e l i n e   B e n o i t
-- 2012-06-16T09:57:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-16/madrid-region-may-cut-public-wages-up-to-3-5-el-pais-says.html
The region of  Madrid  may cut wages
of public sector workers by between 1.8 percent and 3.5 percent,
 El Pais  reported, citing unidentified officials from the
regional government.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Angeline Benoit in Madrid at 
